## IMPORTANT
- The prose rendering function is the most important part — it must correctly split the string at reference positions and wrap them in badge spans
- Handle the case where references overlap or are nested (shouldn't happen but be defensive)
- The textarea in input state should auto-focus
- The Commit button should call POST /api/commit with the compiled data
- After committing, call onCommitted(workflowId) to return to dashboard
- Export as named export
- Keep the component self-contained — fetch its own data, manage its own state
